gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 119, Grizzlies 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Grizzlies, 119-97. Anthony Edwards recorded 24 points, six assists, and five rebounds for the Timberwolves, with Mike Conley adding 18 points and 10 assists in the victory. Jaren Jackson Jr. tallied 18 points, 4 rebounds, and three assists in the losing effort for the Grizzlies. The Timberwolves improve to 12-4 in the regular season, while the Grizzlies fall to 3-13.
